    "For instance, MOB-suite 25 identified canonical features for plasmid replication and conjugation in only 61% of the reference plasmid subtypes we used to train PlasX, which reveals the limits of conventional approaches to identify plasmid features and survey previously undescribed plasmids (Supplementary Table 1)."
